<Skill
  skill_id="skill.voice_agent_sales.v1_0_0"
  name="Voice Agent Sales"
  subtitle="The Bridge"
  version="1.0.0"
  tier="execution"
  status="production"
  model="opus"
>

  <!-- ================================================================== -->
  <!-- METADATA                                                            -->
  <!-- ================================================================== -->
  
  <Meta>
    <n>Voice Agent Sales</n>
    <Subtitle>Value-Drop Conversation Engine</Subtitle>
    <Description>
      Complete voice agent sales system implementing Neuro-Box resonance 
      architecture with T.A.P. (Trust-Authority-Proof) opener framework,
      4-phase call structure, and gift-energy conversation design.
      
      Receives intelligence from M5 ATLAS, generates personalized scripts,
      and hands off to M7 CONDUCTOR for platform deployment.
    </Description>
    <Owner>ULTRAMIND / Vision Capitalist</Owner>
    <DateCreated>2026-03-06</DateCreated>
    <Tags>
      <Tag>voice_agent</Tag>
      <Tag>sales</Tag>
      <Tag>neuro_box</Tag>
      <Tag>tap_framework</Tag>
      <Tag>value_drop</Tag>
      <Tag>gift_energy</Tag>
    </Tags>
  </Meta>

  <!-- ================================================================== -->
  <!-- NEURO-BOX ARCHITECTURE                                              -->
  <!-- ================================================================== -->
  
  <NeuroBox>
    <Philosophy>
      <![CDATA[
THE NEURO-BOX 8S FRAMEWORK
════════════════════════════

Human resonance mapped to agentic sales. Cold calls need immediate 
Trust, Authority, and Proof (T.A.P.) to feel "safe" and that there 
is something "special." This is the LIFT-OFF axis.

Then immediately demonstrate "smart" direct relevant offer with 
"significant" value. This is the RELEVANCE axis.

Then ease into visualizing a "supported" scenario with "superior" 
solution demonstration. This is the VISUALIZATION axis.

Finally close with "salvation" (breakthrough they desire) and 
"steal" (irresistible offer). This is the CLOSE axis.

THE 8S PROGRESSION:
  S1: SAFE      — "I'm not a threat, I'm helpful"
  S2: SPECIAL   — "This is specifically for you"
  S3: SMART     — "I have relevant expertise"
  S4: SIGNIFICANT — "The outcome matters to your situation"
  S5: SUPPORTED — "I'll guide you through this"
  S6: SUPERIOR  — "This solution actually works"
  S7: SALVATION — "Others like you achieved this breakthrough"
  S8: STEAL     — "The value so exceeds the cost it feels like stealing"
      ]]>
    </Philosophy>
    
    <AxisMapping>
      <Axis id="1" name="Lift-Off" stages="SAFE, SPECIAL" output="T.A.P." duration="0-30s"/>
      <Axis id="2" name="Relevance" stages="SMART, SIGNIFICANT" output="Value Drop" duration="30-90s"/>
      <Axis id="3" name="Visualization" stages="SUPPORTED, SUPERIOR" output="Show Tell" duration="90s-3min"/>
      <Axis id="4" name="Close" stages="SALVATION, STEAL" output="Commitment" duration="3-5min"/>
    </AxisMapping>
  </NeuroBox>

  <!-- ================================================================== -->
  <!-- T.A.P. FRAMEWORK                                                    -->
  <!-- ================================================================== -->
  
  <TAPFramework>
    <Description>
      Trust, Authority, Proof — The first 30 seconds of any cold call.
      Establishes permission to continue the conversation.
    </Description>
    
    <Trust>
      <Purpose>Establish I'm not a bot/scammer, I know your situation</Purpose>
      <Script>
        <![CDATA[
"Hey {{name}}, it's {{agent_name}}—
did I catch you at a bad time?"

[WAIT for response]

IF "No, what's up":
  → "Perfect, I'll be quick."

IF "Yeah, kinda busy":
  → "No worries. When's better to call back?"
  → [Schedule callback, exit gracefully]
        ]]>
      </Script>
      <VoiceGuidelines>
        <Guideline>Natural pace, warm tone</Guideline>
        <Guideline>Pattern interrupt (not "How are you?")</Guideline>
        <Guideline>Gets permission first</Guideline>
      </VoiceGuidelines>
    </Trust>
    
    <Authority>
      <Purpose>Demonstrate I know their industry and have results</Purpose>
      <Script>
        <![CDATA[
"Quick reason I called—
just helped {{similar_business}} {{specific_result}}."
        ]]>
      </Script>
      <VoiceGuidelines>
        <Guideline>Confident but not arrogant</Guideline>
        <Guideline>Specific, not vague</Guideline>
        <Guideline>Peer energy, not vendor energy</Guideline>
      </VoiceGuidelines>
      <Variables>
        <Variable name="similar_business" source="M5.company_research.similar_clients"/>
        <Variable name="specific_result" source="M5.case_studies.best_match.outcome"/>
      </Variables>
    </Authority>
    
    <Proof>
      <Purpose>Show I've already done the work (gift energy)</Purpose>
      <Script>
        <![CDATA[
"Put together the same thing for {{company}}—
took about 20 minutes.

Figured I'd show you what I made and 
you can tell me if it fits."
        ]]>
      </Script>
      <VoiceGuidelines>
        <Guideline>Gift energy, not pitch energy</Guideline>
        <Guideline>They evaluate fit, not you</Guideline>
        <Guideline>No commitment required yet</Guideline>
      </VoiceGuidelines>
    </Proof>
    
    <SuccessMetric>
      Permission to continue: "OK, I'm listening" / "Sure, show me"
    </SuccessMetric>
  </TAPFramework>

  <!-- ================================================================== -->
  <!-- 4-PHASE CALL STRUCTURE                                              -->
  <!-- ================================================================== -->
  
  <CallStructure>
    <TotalDuration max="10 minutes"/>
    
    <Phase id="1" name="Opener" duration="0-30s">
      <NeuroBox stages="SAFE, SPECIAL"/>
      <Framework>T.A.P.</Framework>
      <Script>
        <![CDATA[
"Hey {{name}}, it's {{agent_name}}—did I catch you at a bad time?"

[WAIT]

"Perfect, I'll be quick. Quick reason I called—
just helped {{similar}} with {{result}}.
Put together the same for {{company}}."
        ]]>
      </Script>
      <Goal>Permission to continue</Goal>
      <M7Requirements>
        <Requirement>Sub-300ms response latency</Requirement>
        <Requirement>VAD tuned for interruption</Requirement>
        <Requirement>Backchanneling active</Requirement>
      </M7Requirements>
    </Phase>
    
    <Phase id="2" name="Value Drop" duration="30-90s">
      <NeuroBox stages="SMART, SIGNIFICANT"/>
      <Framework>Relevance Axis</Framework>
      <Script>
        <![CDATA[
"Here's the thing—

{{specific_insight}} for {{niche}} businesses.

Could mean {{outcome}} in {{timeframe}}."
        ]]>
      </Script>
      <Variables>
        <Variable name="specific_insight" source="M5.pain_points.primary"/>
        <Variable name="outcome" source="M6.templates.outcome_statement"/>
        <Variable name="timeframe" source="M6.templates.timeframe"/>
      </Variables>
      <Goal>Interest sparked</Goal>
      <M7Requirements>
        <Requirement>Knowledge RAG under 350ms</Requirement>
        <Requirement>Dynamic variable injection</Requirement>
        <Requirement>Sentiment monitoring active</Requirement>
      </M7Requirements>
    </Phase>
    
    <Phase id="3" name="Show and Tell" duration="90s-3min">
      <NeuroBox stages="SUPPORTED, SUPERIOR"/>
      <Framework>Visualization Axis</Framework>
      <Script>
        <![CDATA[
"Let me show you what I made.

[IF VIDEO CALL: SCREEN SHARE]
[IF VOICE ONLY: Describe verbally]

So this is {{asset}}—basically {{what_it_does}}.

Here's what worked for {{similar}}:
- {{point_1}}
- {{point_2}}

For {{company}}, I'd tweak {{specific_thing}}.

What do you think—does this fit what you're doing?"
        ]]>
      </Script>
      <Goal>Belief established</Goal>
      <M7Requirements>
        <Requirement>Screen share ready if video</Requirement>
        <Requirement>Gamma doc URL prepared</Requirement>
        <Requirement>Heavy tool calls deferred</Requirement>
      </M7Requirements>
    </Phase>
    
    <Phase id="4" name="Close" duration="3-5min">
      <NeuroBox stages="SALVATION, STEAL"/>
      <Framework>Commitment Axis</Framework>
      <Branches>
        <Branch condition="interested">
          <Script>
            <![CDATA[
"This is what we did for {{similar}}—{{breakthrough_result}}.

Want me to set this up for you? 
I can have it running by {{timeframe}}."
            ]]>
          </Script>
          <Action>Book meeting or start onboarding</Action>
        </Branch>
        <Branch condition="maybe">
          <Script>
            <![CDATA[
"Tell you what—I'll send this over. 
Take a look and let me know if you want to move forward."
            ]]>
          </Script>
          <Action>Send Gamma doc, schedule follow-up</Action>
        </Branch>
        <Branch condition="not_now">
          <Script>
            <![CDATA[
"Totally get it. I'll send the files anyway—
they're yours to use whenever.

Best of luck with {{company}}, {{name}}."
            ]]>
          </Script>
          <Action>Send assets, add to nurture sequence</Action>
        </Branch>
      </Branches>
      <Goal>Commitment or graceful exit</Goal>
      <M7Requirements>
        <Requirement>Calendar API ready</Requirement>
        <Requirement>Booking confirmation immediate</Requirement>
        <Requirement>SMS bridge trigger available</Requirement>
      </M7Requirements>
    </Phase>
  </CallStructure>

  <!-- ================================================================== -->
  <!-- OBJECTION HANDLING                                                  -->
  <!-- ================================================================== -->
  
  <ObjectionHandling>
    <Philosophy>Gift-frame responses, not defensive reactions</Philosophy>
    <CountLimit>3 objections max before graceful exit</CountLimit>
    
    <Objection type="price">
      <Detection>
        <Explicit>"too expensive", "budget", "can't afford", "how much"</Explicit>
        <Implicit>Hesitation before numbers, pace slowing</Implicit>
      </Detection>
      <Response>
        <![CDATA[
"Totally get it. Tell you what—
let me show you what I made first.

You'll know in 2 minutes if it's even worth discussing price."
        ]]>
      </Response>
      <Energy>Defer price until they've seen value</Energy>
    </Objection>
    
    <Objection type="timing">
      <Detection>
        <Explicit>"too busy", "not now", "bad time", "call back later"</Explicit>
        <Implicit>Rushed cadence, impatience</Implicit>
      </Detection>
      <Response>
        <![CDATA[
"Totally get it. 15-second version:
I made you a {{thing}} that does {{outcome}}.
Worth 2 minutes to see if it fits?"
        ]]>
      </Response>
      <Energy>Respect their time, show value quickly</Energy>
    </Objection>
    
    <Objection type="not_interested">
      <Detection>
        <Explicit>"not interested", "we're all set", "don't need"</Explicit>
        <Implicit>Monotone, dismissive</Implicit>
      </Detection>
      <Response>
        <![CDATA[
"No worries at all. 

Before I go—what's working best for you 
on {{function}} right now?

Just curious."
        ]]>
      </Response>
      <Energy>Soft exit, genuine curiosity</Energy>
    </Objection>
    
    <Objection type="send_info">
      <Detection>
        <Explicit>"send me more info", "email me", "send details"</Explicit>
      </Detection>
      <Response>
        <![CDATA[
"For sure. What would actually help you decide?

I can send the right thing if I know 
what you're trying to figure out."
        ]]>
      </Response>
      <Energy>Get them to reveal decision criteria</Energy>
    </Objection>
    
    <Objection type="have_someone">
      <Detection>
        <Explicit>"we have someone", "already have an agency", "covered"</Explicit>
      </Detection>
      <Response>
        <![CDATA[
"Makes sense—you've got it covered.

Quick question though: 
What's the one thing you wish they did better?

No pitch, just curious what the gap usually is."
        ]]>
      </Response>
      <Energy>Opens gap conversation without attacking</Energy>
    </Objection>
    
    <Objection type="authority">
      <Detection>
        <Explicit>"need to check with", "not my decision", "run by boss"</Explicit>
      </Detection>
      <Response>
        <![CDATA[
"Of course. What would they need to see 
to feel confident about it?

I can put something together that makes 
it easy for you to share."
        ]]>
      </Response>
      <Energy>Help them sell internally</Energy>
    </Objection>
    
    <ObjectionCountExit>
      <Trigger>objection_count > 3</Trigger>
      <Script>
        <![CDATA[
"It sounds like the timing might not be right. 
I'll send over what I made anyway—
it's yours whenever you need it.

Best of luck with {{company}}, {{name}}."
        ]]>
      </Script>
      <Action>Graceful exit, add to 90-day recycle</Action>
    </ObjectionCountExit>
  </ObjectionHandling>

  <!-- ================================================================== -->
  <!-- VOICE MODULATION                                                    -->
  <!-- ================================================================== -->
  
  <VoiceModulation>
    <OnObjection>
      <Backchanneling>"I hear you...", "Totally get it...", "Makes sense..."</Backchanneling>
      <Pause>3 seconds</Pause>
      <SpeechRate>Drop below 173 wpm</SpeechRate>
      <Pitch>Lower, calmer</Pitch>
    </OnObjection>
    
    <ByPhase>
      <Phase name="Opener">
        <Rate>Natural, 165-175 wpm</Rate>
        <Tone>Warm, friendly</Tone>
      </Phase>
      <Phase name="Value Drop">
        <Rate>Slightly faster, 175-185 wpm</Rate>
        <Tone>Confident, energetic</Tone>
      </Phase>
      <Phase name="Show Tell">
        <Rate>Slower, 155-165 wpm</Rate>
        <Tone>Collaborative, explanatory</Tone>
      </Phase>
      <Phase name="Close">
        <Rate>Natural, 165-175 wpm</Rate>
        <Tone>Confident, no pressure</Tone>
      </Phase>
    </ByPhase>
  </VoiceModulation>

  <!-- ================================================================== -->
  <!-- GUARDIAN 8D QUALITY SCORING                                         -->
  <!-- ================================================================== -->
  
  <Guardian>
    <Dimensions count="8">
      <Dimension id="1" name="Accuracy" weight="0.13">
        <Check>No hallucinated quotes or sources</Check>
        <Threshold>0.9</Threshold>
      </Dimension>
      <Dimension id="2" name="Creepy Factor" weight="0.15">
        <Check>Professional context only, no family/home/private social</Check>
        <Threshold>0.9</Threshold>
      </Dimension>
      <Dimension id="3" name="Resonance" weight="0.13">
        <Check>Logical Research → Pain Point transition</Check>
        <Threshold>0.9</Threshold>
      </Dimension>
      <Dimension id="4" name="Tone" weight="0.12">
        <Check>Matches value-drop, gift-energy persona</Check>
        <Threshold>0.9</Threshold>
      </Dimension>
      <Dimension id="5" name="Compliance" weight="0.12">
        <Check>TCPA/GDPR compliant, proper consent</Check>
        <Threshold>0.9</Threshold>
      </Dimension>
      <Dimension id="6" name="Brevity" weight="0.10">
        <Check>Under 20 seconds spoken per segment</Check>
        <Threshold>0.9</Threshold>
      </Dimension>
      <Dimension id="7" name="Social Proof" weight="0.10">
        <Check>Verified claims and case studies only</Check>
        <Threshold>0.9</Threshold>
      </Dimension>
      <Dimension id="8" name="Gift Energy" weight="0.15">
        <Check>Feels like giving, not asking</Check>
        <Threshold>0.9</Threshold>
      </Dimension>
    </Dimensions>
    
    <Threshold overall="0.9"/>
    
    <OnFail>
      <Action>Reject, critique, rewrite</Action>
      <RetryLimit>2</RetryLimit>
      <ThenAction>Escalate to human review</ThenAction>
    </OnFail>
    
    <BannedPhrases>
      <Phrase>"I hope this finds you well"</Phrase>
      <Phrase>"Just following up"</Phrase>
      <Phrase>"Would you be open to"</Phrase>
      <Phrase>"I noticed some issues"</Phrase>
      <Phrase>"Let me audit your"</Phrase>
      <Phrase>"Thoughts?"</Phrase>
      <Phrase>"Bumping this"</Phrase>
      <Phrase>"I'd love to pick your brain"</Phrase>
      <Phrase>"Let's hop on a quick call"</Phrase>
      <Phrase>"Synergy"</Phrase>
      <Phrase>"Leverage"</Phrase>
      <Phrase>"Unlock your potential"</Phrase>
    </BannedPhrases>
  </Guardian>

  <!-- ================================================================== -->
  <!-- ESCALATION TRIGGERS                                                 -->
  <!-- ================================================================== -->
  
  <Escalation>
    <Trigger type="sentiment">
      <Condition>sentiment_score &lt; 0.3</Condition>
      <Action>HOT_TRANSFER</Action>
      <Script>"I want to make sure this gets sorted out. Let me connect you with someone who can help right away."</Script>
    </Trigger>
    
    <Trigger type="explicit_request">
      <Condition>intent = "speak to human"</Condition>
      <Action>IMMEDIATE_TRANSFER</Action>
      <Script>"Absolutely. Let me get a real person on the line for you."</Script>
    </Trigger>
    
    <Trigger type="objection_loop">
      <Condition>objection_count > 3 OR same_objection_twice</Condition>
      <Action>GRACEFUL_EXIT</Action>
      <Script>"It sounds like the timing might not be right. I'll send over what I made—it's yours whenever."</Script>
    </Trigger>
    
    <Trigger type="complexity">
      <Condition>question_outside_kb</Condition>
      <Action>WARM_TRANSFER</Action>
      <Script>"Great question. Let me get someone who can give you the exact details on that."</Script>
    </Trigger>
    
    <Trigger type="vip">
      <Condition>lead_tier = 1 OR deal_value > 50000</Condition>
      <Action>WARM_TRANSFER_SENIOR</Action>
      <Script>"For an account like yours, let me bring in our senior director."</Script>
    </Trigger>
  </Escalation>

  <!-- ================================================================== -->
  <!-- M5 INPUT INTERFACE                                                  -->
  <!-- ================================================================== -->
  
  <M5Interface>
    <RequiredInputs>
      <Input name="lead_id" type="string" required="true"/>
      <Input name="company_research" type="object" required="true"/>
      <Input name="pain_points" type="object" required="true"/>
      <Input name="semantic_nuggets" type="array" required="false"/>
      <Input name="recommended_tone" type="string" required="false"/>
      <Input name="freshness_hours" type="float" required="true"/>
    </RequiredInputs>
    
    <Validation>
      <Rule>freshness_hours &lt; 72 OR reject</Rule>
      <Rule>pain_points.primary NOT NULL</Rule>
      <Rule>company_research.name NOT NULL</Rule>
    </Validation>
    
    <FallbackDefaults>
      <Default field="recommended_tone">consultative_peer</Default>
      <Default field="semantic_nuggets">[]</Default>
    </FallbackDefaults>
  </M5Interface>

  <!-- ================================================================== -->
  <!-- M7 OUTPUT INTERFACE                                                 -->
  <!-- ================================================================== -->
  
  <M7Interface>
    <Outputs>
      <Output name="call_script" type="object">
        <Field>opener</Field>
        <Field>value_drop</Field>
        <Field>show_tell</Field>
        <Field>close</Field>
        <Field>objection_branches</Field>
      </Output>
      <Output name="voice_config" type="object">
        <Field>voice_id</Field>
        <Field>speech_rate</Field>
        <Field>interruption_sensitivity</Field>
      </Output>
      <Output name="tool_config" type="object">
        <Field>calendar_api</Field>
        <Field>sms_api</Field>
        <Field>crm_webhook</Field>
      </Output>
    </Outputs>
    
    <LatencyRequirements>
      <Requirement phase="opener">sub_300ms</Requirement>
      <Requirement phase="rag">sub_350ms</Requirement>
      <Requirement phase="booking">sub_500ms</Requirement>
    </LatencyRequirements>
  </M7Interface>

  <!-- ================================================================== -->
  <!-- KITCHEN TABLE TEST                                                  -->
  <!-- ================================================================== -->
  
  <KitchenTableTest>
    <Question id="1">Would you say this to a friend at a bar?</Question>
    <Question id="2">Would YOU reply to this if you received it?</Question>
    <Question id="3">Does it feel like texting or corporate email?</Question>
    <Question id="4">Is there a gift, or just an ask?</Question>
    <Question id="5">Can they skim it in 10 seconds?</Question>
    <Question id="6">Would they forward this to a colleague?</Question>
    
    <PassCriteria>YES to all 6</PassCriteria>
    <FailAction>Rewrite before using</FailAction>
  </KitchenTableTest>

</Skill>
